Package com.googlecode.batchfb.err

Exception Summary
FacebookException Root of the exception hierarchy for BatchFB.
IOFacebookException Thrown when a request to facebook times out or produces a http error code or returns totally bogus data.
OAuthAccessTokenException Indicates something is wrong with the access token you have (or should have) passed to Facebook.
OAuthException Indicates something has failed in the authorization of your application.
PermissionException Thrown when trying to do something that produces a permission error.
QueryParseException Indicates that there was something wrong with the construction of a request to facebook.
